Titolo: Knights of Pen & Paper

Anno: 2012

Descrizione: Knights of Pen & Paper is a role-playing video game developed by Behold Studios and published by Paradox Interactive. It was released on October 30, 2012, for iOS and Android, and on June 18, 2013, for Windows, Mac OS X and Linux. Versions for PlayStation 4 and Xbox One were released on December 13, 2018. A Nintendo Switch version was released on May 29, 2018, in North America and on November 21, 2019, in Japan.The game received positive reviews from critics, who cited its originality.